that feeling when you're lvl 11 and xins 0-4 and lvl 8, then he gets this item and can STILL out all-in you unless you also have rageblade. 

Never have I had less fun playing toplane Blitzcrunk. Then I bought Rageblade on him. Hell, I've seen people bullying top lane with shit like Rageblade Nunu. 

